Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.62,0:00:12.05,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.44,0:00:13.04,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.60,0:00:16.64,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hirono-kun is a person who will treat me well. {Hirono's one night stand with Miyako...}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.17,0:00:18.30,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.50,0:00:23.11,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Now I... I only want to be around people who treasure me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.11,0:00:25.11,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,If that's not what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.11,0:00:26.89,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,then it's better off to be alone.{orig: Being alone is better.}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.20,0:00:28.17,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Miyako...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.51,0:00:31.43,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to disappear from someone's heart anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.70,0:00:34.52,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,If that happens, it's better not to meet in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.24,0:00:44.28,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Can I stay here? {Is it ok, if I stay here?}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.61,0:00:45.70,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.86,0:00:48.83,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever happens, will you only look at me?{When ever it is, will you look only at me?}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.13,0:00:49.87,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.03,0:00:53.87,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I no longer want to lose things precious to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.13,0:01:24.82,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?{What is the meaning of this?}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.06,0:01:26.24,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Kei...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.46,0:01:27.70,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,So it's like this?{Thing like this that.}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.59,0:01:30.83,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan's...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.88,0:01:45.50,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Kei!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.35,0:01:54.83,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.69,0:02:02.60,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Miyako.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.96,0:02:05.24,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Please, don't go.{Don't go, I beg of you.}{Please, don't go}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.58,0:02:06.24,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.69,0:02:08.24,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Me or her, who are you going to choose? {check}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.19,0:02:10.99,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You won't go, right, Hirono-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.34,0:02:16.20,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Look at me only and no one else other than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.76,0:02:18.05,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Miyako...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.05,0:02:19.30,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.36,0:02:31.67,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for a bit, I'll be right back. {Hirono, you bastard! You left a girl hanging >_>}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.37,0:02:38.16,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,, In the end, you're going. {check}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.67,0:02:45.56,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Kei-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.64,0:02:48.64,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me alone!{Mind your own business!}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.79,0:02:52.28,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want to film it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.46,0:02:54.57,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You want to film it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.97,0:02:56.21,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Film it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.18,0:02:59.58,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's good if you film it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.58,0:03:02.29,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,There won't be another chance when something like this happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.29,0:03:03.76,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Film it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.00,0:03:05.32,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Kei-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.46,0:03:23.46,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Kei... {thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.58,0:03:26.18,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.45,0:03:28.54,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I'm searching right now... {for Kei}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.54,0:03:29.82,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,For Kei-chan? {For Kei-chan?}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.93,0:03:32.33,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Can you meet up with me for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.70,0:03:37.21,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What is it all of a sudden?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.21,0:03:41.16,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What are you thinking, Hirono?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.45,0:03:43.10,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.76,0:03:46.61,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You, going out with Miyamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.61,0:03:48.50,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What does that have to do with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.88,0:03:50.75,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Then what's with Kei-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.23,0:03:52.98,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.98,0:03:55.67,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Me and Kei are nothing like th- {nothing like that}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.05,0:03:57.75,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.75,0:04:00.28,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You're half-assed. {I don't know, "half-assed is all I could come up with}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.28,0:04:01.51,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Your studying is half-assed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.51,0:04:03.00,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Your working is half-assed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.30,0:04:05.79,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess with people by being like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.79,0:04:08.14,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Stop saying senseless things!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.56,0:04:11.20,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You think you can beat me with your left hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.53,0:04:12.69,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The right is for work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.24,0:04:14.44,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Even your fighting is half-assed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.63,0:04:15.40,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.73,0:04:18.05,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You're running away from everything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.05,0:04:19.41,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I have never run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.41,0:04:22.92,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Without any thought, you get close and drag it out. {check}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.92,0:04:25.38,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's just the same as running away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.01,0:04:30.47,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Your old man... Didn't you run away instead of trying to persuade him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.64,0:04:33.01,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,How can you even understand about my family?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.23,0:04:34.63,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Which side is Kei-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.81,0:04:37.56,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Family, or a woman to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.67,0:04:39.71,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Neither, Kei is Kei!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.86,0:04:42.24,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I said don't be half-assed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.24,0:04:44.97,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you're not sure is the reason that Kei-chan is crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.11,0:04:48.57,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Because of your indecisive attitude and running away,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.57,0:04:50.91,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,that girl is suffering.{That girl is in pain.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.54,0:04:53.20,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,If this keeps up, that girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.20,0:04:58.25,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,will only keep crying, and follow you like a stray.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.50,0:05:03.75,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Only you, Hirono, can rescue that girl's feelings{emotions}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.40,0:05:08.79,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.67,0:05:10.89,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Miyako?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.16,0:05:21.43,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Miyako...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.24,0:05:25.42,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hirono-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.42,0:05:26.48,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Miyako.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.48,0:05:28.08,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.08,0:05:28.97,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.97,0:05:31.41,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Let's stop seeing each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.85,0:05:33.74,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying, Miyako?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.98,0:05:35.65,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,For me now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.65,0:05:38.42,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,it hurts to think about Hirono-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.26,0:05:41.53,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I know that I'm saying whatever I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.53,0:05:43.70,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,And sometimes it's not always the right thing.{I also know that that is not right also.}{reword please}{Aiko:}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.70,0:05:44.90,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.14,0:05:49.04,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hirono-kun's heart isn't mine and mine alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.29,0:05:50.72,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Miyako...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.72,0:05:54.88,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, when Hirono-kun's heart fills with other things, then I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.88,0:05:57.39,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,will disappear again, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.39,0:05:58.88,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.88,0:06:00.81,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Let's break up before that happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.81,0:06:02.54,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Miyako!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.54,0:06:03.82,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Miyako!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.08,0:06:13.81,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Miyako?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.20,0:06:24.61,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hiro-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.57,0:06:26.89,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.32,0:06:29.63,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here? {I don't know why, I like this character for some reason >_>}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.82,0:06:31.09,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.{For no reason}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.09,0:06:34.20,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,How was the sandwich that Kei-senpai made?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.71,0:06:38.66,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,She called suddenly last night and asked how to make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.67,0:06:39.96,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so jealous! {check}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.96,0:06:40.39,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Oww oww oww~ {do I need to translate the "ow"?}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.61,0:06:42.30,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Just what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.30,0:06:44.30,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Since she suddenly started cooking...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.45,0:06:46.63,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I asked why because I thought it was strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.63,0:06:48.53,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Then, without hesitation,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.53,0:06:49.89,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"For Onii-chan," {"For sake of Onii-chan}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.00,0:06:51.64,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,was what she said!{And says such things!}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.93,0:06:53.64,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, she was blushing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.64,0:06:56.68,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,So I had no choice. For Kei-senpai's happiness,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.68,0:06:59.35,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I taught her how to make it with tears in my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.35,0:07:01.07,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.38,0:07:04.73,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there was something that I received in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.73,0:07:05.57,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.00,0:07:08.08,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,A postcard for the monthly MIMI.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.50,0:07:12.30,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,This month's issue's reader prizes are very luxurious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.03,0:07:14.71,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.71,0:07:15.69,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.69,0:07:17.24,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a Shindou Nagi fan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.60,0:07:20.17,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, since the name is similar to Kei-senpai. {the way Hayama squirm is so cute >_> I want a Kohai like that lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.37,0:07:21.48,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.48,0:07:27.63,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The interesting work is another author?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.63,0:07:31.60,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Because Shindou Nagi is boring nowadays.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.98,0:07:35.24,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's as if his enthusiasm has disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.24,0:07:38.41,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Before it was more upbeat. {check}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.08,0:07:41.12,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's been too plain recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.12,0:07:43.65,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Shindou Nagi's uniqueness disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.05,0:07:47.11,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Still, Hirono-senpai doesn't really know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.57,0:07:49.07,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.21,0:07:55.12,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All half-assed. {thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.27,0:07:59.57,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I already know, or something like that. {thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.76,0:08:13.37,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Just knowing something, and understanding something are different.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.91,0:08:15.53,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I know that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.64,0:08:19.57,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Because everything is important,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.57,0:08:21.97,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,you don't want to lose everything, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.97,0:08:24.18,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.18,0:08:27.45,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,But still, someday you need to give up one side...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.09,0:08:31.04,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,in order not to lose the most important thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.13,0:08:33.04,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I said that everything is important. {check}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.64,0:08:35.08,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,But if you don't decide,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.08,0:08:37.30,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,you will lose everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.30,0:08:38.52,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you say that,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.52,0:08:42.09,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I can't treat something like it never happened and throw it away! {check}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.09,0:08:44.04,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You're not throwing it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.94,0:08:51.05,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You're being asked to throw it away. {check}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.32,0:08:55.31,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's why it hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.38,0:09:00.15,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like getting hurt anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.79,0:09:02.48,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,But as long as you are alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.48,0:09:04.65,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,you can't run away from pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.56,0:09:07.83,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.94,0:09:10.35,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I know those things, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.35,0:09:12.89,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,To untie the bonds of a relationship once made...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.89,0:09:16.04,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,the same amount of pain will come with it. {check}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.03,0:09:20.40,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Can all of you withstand it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.40,0:09:21.79,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we can't withstand it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.79,0:09:23.47,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,we can't run away from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.20,0:09:26.68,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.74,0:09:37.41,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, the answer was already decided from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.71,0:09:39.43,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I had the answer...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.75,0:09:42.34,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't have the courage to understand the meaning of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.90,0:09:46.19,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.03,0:09:50.77,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,feel like I found the color that I was looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.60,0:10:07.29,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Kei, are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.02,0:10:10.61,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.84,0:10:12.71,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You forgot your crutch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.71,0:10:13.91,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.91,0:10:15.84,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Since your leg is broken, you shouldn't overdo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.84,0:10:17.42,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's not your concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.76,0:10:20.98,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Kei... thanks for the sandwiches.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.77,0:10:26.60,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I ran into Hayama and heard...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.60,0:10:29.96,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I heard that my manga was boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.56,0:10:36.49,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Kei, I'm thinking of leaving school and devoting my time to working on manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.75,0:10:41.09,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Up until now, it was wrong just to work with partial effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.09,0:10:44.96,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I'm not good enough to do anything if I don't do it with my full effort.{check}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.74,0:10:48.98,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Does this have anything to do with Miyamura-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.98,0:10:52.22,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,No, it was something I thought about myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.53,0:10:53.88,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Have you already made your decision?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.88,0:10:54.97,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.52,0:10:59.23,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so? That's just how you are, Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.78,0:11:04.66,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,In everything, you decided for yourself what to do and would go at it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.60,0:11:06.24,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Kei...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.46,0:11:13.01,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,In order to follow your dreams, no matter how difficult it was, you stood by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.01,0:11:14.36,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It was only after you saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.67,0:11:15.36,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.69,0:11:24.37,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Before you started calling me Onii-chan, in order to make you happy, I started drawing manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.66,0:11:26.16,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.07,0:11:32.02,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It was fun back then, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.47,0:11:35.60,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember... when we got into a fight right after you read my manga?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.67,0:11:36.87,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.95,0:11:39.72,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What was that about again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.72,0:11:43.11,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Things really took a sudden turn. That was a shock, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.52,0:11:48.45,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Me, you and Chihiro argued back and forth over what was good or bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.66,0:11:52.70,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan, in the end, you looked at it from the perspective of a rejected girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.00,0:11:56.67,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I didn't listen to you as to the problems with that, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.67,0:12:01.54,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's because I didn't think you did enough for a good ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.91,0:12:04.71,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it, we never finished it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.33,0:12:09.54,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Although, even without thinking about it, we were really serious about the ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.03,0:12:13.13,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That ending was like reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.13,0:12:14.33,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.51,0:12:19.65,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't a standard happy ending. To cut it short like that makes it more realistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.65,0:12:23.52,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, the end just visits suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.23,0:12:30.03,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Like myself who was a fool looking at a dream, everything just crumbled down suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.33,0:12:30.98,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Kei...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.98,0:12:31.82,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.24,0:12:35.28,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let it end...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.10,0:12:36.99,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Kei...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.23,0:12:41.99,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I've always, always thought that things would stay the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.99,0:12:44.58,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan is here. I am here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.58,0:12:48.87,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,We support each other even when I'm being unreasonable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.32,0:12:52.25,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,But I did my best to support you, and when I was down, you supported me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.25,0:12:55.79,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Though we sometimes fought, we always made up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.79,0:13:02.48,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,And then, we'd go from being like brother and sister to being lovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.48,0:13:04.21,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'd get married...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.21,0:13:06.41,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,And have kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.41,0:13:07.61,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I've always...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.25,0:13:11.02,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I've always gone on believing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.98,0:13:13.20,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Kei...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.60,0:13:17.48,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan, what about you? Please tell me the truth.{Onii-chan, what did you think? Please tell me the truth.}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.21,0:13:21.62,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I also thought about it along the same lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.62,0:13:24.05,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow or another I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.14,0:13:25.34,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.96,0:13:30.98,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I just realized it a bit too late then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.19,0:13:34.39,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It would have been better if I had confessed my feelings sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.00,0:13:37.05,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Kei...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.74,0:13:41.09,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan! I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.98,0:13:47.42,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I love you! I've always loved you, Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.85,0:13:51.56,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since I was little, I've always...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.32,0:13:54.64,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I've always yearned for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.73,0:13:57.76,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You were my pride. {Hirono was someone Kei could be proud of}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.75,0:14:01.83,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I've always... always wanted to say, "I love you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.40,0:14:09.99,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go back...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.35,0:14:13.33,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,To when I was always with Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.33,0:14:16.54,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The time when I called you Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.10,0:14:18.25,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,We can go back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.69,0:14:20.96,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back, Kei!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.96,0:14:24.00,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,We might not be related, but you are my little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.00,0:14:26.04,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You are very important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.04,0:14:26.64,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.41,0:14:31.61,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I guess...{Aiko: I think something a little more profound than So...}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.70,0:14:34.65,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,you were in pain as well, Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.00,0:14:38.40,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.66,0:14:39.66,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Kei...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.31,0:14:42.59,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.59,0:14:46.59,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,, It might take a while, but I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.73,0:14:54.98,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I guess this is the end for here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.53,0:14:57.01,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Are you running away again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.30,0:14:59.45,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, it's just like it was before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.45,0:15:01.72,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,If it's something you don't want to face, you can just close your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.72,0:15:04.42,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,If it's something you don't want to hear, you can just cover your ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.42,0:15:06.89,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I've always done, and that's how I live.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.09,0:15:09.31,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You won't obtain anything that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.31,0:15:12.57,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. From the beginning, I didn't have much hope anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.79,0:15:15.47,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,But, he is doing his best.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.47,0:15:19.22,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be strong in Hirono-kun's eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.22,0:15:22.11,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's too bad. I wanted to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.11,0:15:22.66,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.86,0:15:26.66,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,My dream of seeing someone like me possibly finding happiness...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.10,0:15:30.30,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,A dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.44,0:15:40.68,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Miyako?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.68,0:15:41.68,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.68,0:15:42.88,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.88,0:15:43.52,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell you. {Aiko: Secret for sake of time}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.85,0:15:45.05,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Can we meet up and talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.05,0:15:47.36,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,No way. It will make my resolve weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.51,0:15:48.62,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Resolve?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.62,0:15:50.77,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You see, I'm going to leave this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.77,0:15:53.01,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,, I'm going to go somewhere where no one will find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.37,0:15:54.86,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Miyako...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.86,0:15:56.90,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,This call will be the last.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.90,0:16:00.54,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,This is my last goodbye to Hirono-kun who has always been kind to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.54,0:16:01.53,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Miyako...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.85,0:16:06.19,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You see, I think up until now I've been testing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.19,0:16:07.19,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Testing me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.37,0:16:10.03,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since we met that Christmas night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.34,0:16:12.87,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,At that time, I wanted to see what your reaction would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.74,0:16:17.55,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I wondered if Hirono-kun would take care of me or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.93,0:16:20.37,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's not something worth just to test.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.64,0:16:24.21,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,If it wasn't the case, then I wouldn't want to be involved with anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.77,0:16:26.74,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Well, how did I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.74,0:16:27.05,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.43,0:16:29.89,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Did I fail based on my test results?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.05,0:16:31.72,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,No, you passed with flying colors.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.72,0:16:34.57,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hirono-kun is someone that is too good for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.57,0:16:35.57,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.01,0:16:38.39,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I have a good eye for judging people. {see has a good eye for looking out for people, judging people, bascially determining if the people is good or bad}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.39,0:16:41.02,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, why do you want to leave town?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.02,0:16:44.07,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want to be erased from Hirono-kun's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.25,0:16:46.91,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'll disappear first while you still love me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.91,0:16:48.22,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Miyako...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.22,0:16:50.84,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You see, at home there was no sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.84,0:16:51.57,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.88,0:16:54.41,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,My parents were very distant, you know. {is aloof the right term for someone that is quiet, tolerant, inexpressive?}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.41,0:16:57.25,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,My mom and dad couldn't get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.25,0:16:59.22,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,They never talked.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.22,0:17:02.93,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It seemed that there wasn't ever the sound of talking or even footsteps heard inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.93,0:17:07.45,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,They only thought about the things they disliked about each other, paying no attention to their daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.56,0:17:08.59,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,And my name...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.59,0:17:09.61,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Name?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.61,0:17:12.42,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,They wouldn't even say my name at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.78,0:17:19.95,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how good my grades were or if I was first in sports, they wouldn't say anything to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.95,0:17:23.89,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I even worked hard to learn Mom and Dad's favorite fish recipe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.89,0:17:26.10,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Anything to get any affection from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.10,0:17:26.60,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.27,0:17:28.44,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Miyako...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.44,0:17:30.02,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's weird, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.02,0:17:35.12,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,There was no reason to pretend, but I also lived while hiding my breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.28,0:17:37.96,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, six years ago they divorced.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.96,0:17:39.80,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I was relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.80,0:17:42.62,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I suddenly felt liberated.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.62,0:17:48.30,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,, I left home and thought I'd go wherever I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.30,0:17:52.14,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that I would one day, somewhere, find the place where I belonged.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.54,0:17:56.42,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Though I was by myself, I felt relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.42,0:18:00.64,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't need to prevent myself from being tired or hated. {better way to say this?}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.64,0:18:03.48,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I chose to go some place whenever I wanted, wherever I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.02,0:18:07.66,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I was a person that could go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.22,0:18:11.00,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,But... But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.46,0:18:14.84,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Being able to go anywhere means that there is no place to belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.57,0:18:20.50,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Not having a place to go or go back to, it was... like being alone in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.78,0:18:21.83,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.83,0:18:22.34,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.87,0:18:25.18,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk like that by yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.18,0:18:26.18,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hirono-kun...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.69,0:18:30.31,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you say so in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.31,0:18:31.43,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You've been lonely, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.43,0:18:32.70,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You've been in pain, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.70,0:18:34.67,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Then you should've said that to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.67,0:18:36.36,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I could say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.36,0:18:38.69,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,If I did, then Hirono-kun would pity me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.69,0:18:42.19,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What I want isn't pity, but rather for someone to treasure me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.50,0:18:45.03,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I will be the place where you can be!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.10,0:18:50.69,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, all that stuff about you being alone will be of the past. Isn't that good enough?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.22,0:18:54.20,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Even if there is a place for me, I'm scared of it disappearing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.20,0:18:55.48,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That won't happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.48,0:18:57.37,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,How can you say it like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.37,0:18:58.55,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Believe in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.55,0:19:00.83,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I want to believe... I want to...!{I want to believe... I want to believe...}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.83,0:19:02.05,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What are you so worried about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.05,0:19:06.25,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'm horrible, that's why. Someday you'll just push me away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.25,0:19:07.71,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That won't happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.71,0:19:11.15,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I knew about the feelings that you and Kei-chan had for each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.15,0:19:13.39,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that I couldn't win against Kei-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.63,0:19:18.59,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,But I wanted to be with you so much; I desperately clung to you, Hirono-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.59,0:19:21.38,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,And therefore, I also knew about the pain you felt inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.38,0:19:25.73,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'm horrible. I could only think about myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.73,0:19:27.57,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I will think about my own situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.57,0:19:31.41,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That should be enough for you! That is who you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.01,0:19:34.91,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I will answer for my own situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.91,0:19:36.07,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,After that, it is up to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.76,0:19:38.91,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really all right to believe in you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.44,0:19:39.90,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.44,0:19:42.74,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to disappear anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.74,0:19:45.58,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'm right here. I no longer want to be ignored!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.76,0:19:48.42,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always be watching you. There's no way that you'll disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.42,0:19:54.10,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I want to stay! I want you to eat my cooking while it's warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.39,0:19:55.92,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be involved with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.54,0:19:59.26,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,For me, being dumped by someone... {probably implied that she no longer wish to be dumped by people she love.}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.63,0:20:01.82,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,When you get good grades, I'll say that it's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.26,0:20:04.05,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,If you do wrong, I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.05,0:20:05.44,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,And of course I'll eat your cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.11,0:20:09.61,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how pathetic it is, I want to be by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.61,0:20:11.12,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You can do things the way you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.50,0:20:12.94,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'll accept everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.94,0:20:14.94,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hirono-kun, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.94,0:20:15.78,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Miyako, listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.38,0:20:18.62,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I... About you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.01,0:21:02.87,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.43,0:21:04.57,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.28,0:21:10.43,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hirono-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.72,0:21:12.38,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know places like this...{I don't know, places like this.}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.00,0:21:15.33,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I looked around all the phone booths in Otowa. {otowa is the town name}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.67,0:21:16.84,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hirono-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.17,0:21:18.17,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Miyako!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.85,0:21:42.56,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You have a responsibility now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.56,0:21:43.60,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Responsibility?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.60,0:21:46.00,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You caught me, so don't ever let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.44,0:21:48.99,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you not like being bound with someone this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.19,0:21:52.13,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,A person's feelings can change.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.58,0:23:39.80,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starting to return to the memories that have not yet faded.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.80,0:23:43.40,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Next {\i1}ef - a tale of memories:{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.40,0:23:44.83,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ever forever.{\i0}
